name: Snow Bunny Canyon
description:
Introduction

Approach

Park at Winter Cabin T/H at the end of FR 538 and start the approach there.

Descent

The canyon has a handful of rappels and down climbs. A 100ft rope and pull will get you through the canyon.

Exit

Coming out of Snow Bunny head left down Sycamore Canyon, boulder hoping until you reach Winter Cabin Trail #70 and head back up to Winter cabin and your vehicle.
